<h1>Burns Depression Checklist</h1>

<p>Instructions: indicate how much you have
experienced each symptom during the past week, including today.
Please answer all 25 items.</p>

<ul>
  <li>0 = Not at all</li>
  <li>1 = Somewhat</li>
  <li>2 = Moderately</li>
  <li>3 = A lot</li>
  <li>4 = Extremely</li>
</ul>

<%= simple_form_for @survey do |f| %>
<h1>Thoughts and Feelings</h1>
<h2>1. Feeling sad or down in the dumps</h2>
  <%= f.input :question_0, label: false, collection: 0..4, as: :range, input_html:{ min:"0", max:"4",step:"1", list:"question_0"} %>
<h2>2. Feeling unhappy or blue</h2>
  <%= f.input :question_1, label: false, collection: 0..4, as: :range, input_html:{ min:"0", max:"4",step:"1", list:"question_1"} %>
<h2>3. Crying spells or tearfulness</h2>
